These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, spanish, british, indian
There 4 different types of food: orange, banana, pineapple, onion
1. the person eating onion is on the left of the british##1
2. the thai is on the left of the person eating banana##1
3. the indian is in an odd position##4
4. the person eating pineapple is on the left or right of the person eating onion##3
5. the thai is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Nationality   | thai | spanish | indian | british |
| Food        | orange | banana   | onion | pineapple    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, country, reggae, folk
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, ferret, hedgehog, lizard
1. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of folk##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the goldfish is the fan of punk##1
5. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
6. the owner of the goldfish is the fan of punk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | punk  | country  | folk |
| Pet   | lizard    | goldfish | hedgehog | ferret    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, brown, orange, ebony
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, entrepreneur, analyst, freelancer
1. the person who likes ebony is on the left or right of the freelancer##3
2. the person who likes orange is in an even position##4
3. the freelancer is on the left or right of the person who likes brown##3
4. the freelancer is on the right of the analyst##1
5. the accountant is in an odd position##4
6. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person who likes orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Color          | ebony | orange | brown    | ivory      |
| Job   | analyst        | freelancer     | accountant | entrepreneur |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
4 different pets are kept: frog, pony, horse, dog
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, helicopter, boat, motorbike
1. the owner of the pony is between the person driving the skateboard and the person driving the motorbike##2
2. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
3. the person driving the boat is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Pet         | dog | frog | pony | horse |
| Transport   | boat       | skateboard   | helicopter    | motorbike  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
4 different pets are kept: bird, mouse, pony, cat
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, crime, family, mystery
1. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
2. the person watching crime movies is the owner of the cat##1
3. the person watching family movies is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
4. the owner of the mouse is on the far left##1
5. the owner of the pony is in an odd position##4
6. the person watching thriller movies is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Pet   | mouse  | bird    | pony   | cat       |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | mystery | family | crime |

