.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, analyst, social-worker, project-manager
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, bellflower, azalea, iris
1. the person who growsbellflower is in an even position##4
2. the project-manager is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
3. the social-worker is in an odd position##4
4. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the mechanic##1
5. the person who growsazalea is on the left or right of the person who growsmarigold##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Job   | social-worker      | analyst | project-manager | mechanic |
| Flower   | iris | bellflower     | marigold  | azalea  |

