.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
City: hannover, marseilles, san-francisco, miami
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, techno, gospel, disco
1. the fan of disco is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of rock##1
3. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
4. the fan of disco is the person traveling to hannover##1
5. the person traveling to miami is on the left or right of the fan of rock##3
6. the fan of techno is on the right of the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| City   | hannover | miami | san-francisco | marseilles    |
| Music-Genre     | disco | gospel  | rock     | techno |

