.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
House: cottage, townhouse, craftsman, art-deco
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, nigerian, polish, american
1. the american is on the left or right of the townhouse house##3
2. the art-deco house is in an odd position##4
3. the american is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3
4. the art-deco house is on the right of the american##1
5. the cottage house is between the art-deco house and the townhouse house##2
6. the nigerian is in an odd position##4
7. the nigerian is between the cottage house and the polish##2
8. the cottage house is on the left or right of the townhouse house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| House   | townhouse | cottage      | art-deco | craftsman |
| Nationality   | japanese  | american | nigerian    | polish            |

