.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, dutch, mexican, australian
The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, photographer, lawyer, designer
1. the mexican is on the left or right of the egyptian##3
2. the egyptian is on the right of the dutch##1
3. the mechanic is between the photographer and the mexican##2
4. the mechanic is in an odd position##4
5. the mexican is the lawyer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Nationality   | australian | dutch   | egyptian | mexican |
| Job    | designer     | photographer | mechanic     | lawyer  |

