.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, light-blue, amber, apricot
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, bus, trike, boat
1. the person who likes fuchsia is the person driving the boat##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
3. the person driving the boat is between the person driving the snowmobile and the person who likes amber##2
4. the person who likes fuchsia is in an odd position##4
5. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3
6. the person who likes light-blue is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Color      | light-blue       | amber   | fuchsia | apricot |
| Transport   | trike | bus | boat        | snowmobile    |

