.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, poppy, sunflower, marigold
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, argentine, chinese, british
1. the nigerian is in an even position##4
2. the chinese is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
3. the chinese is on the left of the british##1
4. the british is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
5. the person who growspoppy is on the left or right of the person who growssunflower##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Flower   | zinnia   | marigold   | poppy      | sunflower      |
| Nationality      | argentine | chinese | british | nigerian |

