.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-12::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, lacrosse, skateboarding, soccer
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, bolivar, dunhill, aristoff
1. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
2. the dunhill-smoker is in an even position##4
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the bolivar-smoker and the dunhill-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Sport          | soccer | lacrosse  | skateboarding  | biathlon |
| Cigar   | aristoff  | dunhill | montecristo | bolivar   |

