.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, iced-tea, coffee, water
There 4 different types of food: peas, cauliflower, cabbage, banana
1. the person eating cauliflower is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating peas is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
3. the person eating cauliflower is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
4. the person drinking iced-tea is in an odd position##4
5. the person eating cauliflower is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |     4     |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | juice | coffee | water  |
| Food     | cauliflower   | peas  | banana  | cabbage |

