.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-14::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, backgammon, snooker, whist
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, videographer, fisherman, mechanic
1. the fisherman is in an odd position##4
2. the person playing monopoly is in an odd position##4
3. the person playing whist is on the left of the fisherman##1
4. the lawyer is on the right of the mechanic##1
5. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
6. the lawyer is on the left or right of the mechanic##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4       |
| Game   | snooker | whist | monopoly | backgammon |
| Job           | mechanic     | lawyer     | fisherman   | videographer         |

