.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, april, december, june
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, teacher, lawyer, entrepreneur
1. the person who's birthday is in july is between the fisherman and the person who's birthday is in april##2
2. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
5. the entrepreneur is in an odd position##4
6. the lawyer is on the left of the teacher##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Birthday   | june | april         | july   | december |
| Job   | lawyer    | teacher | entrepreneur | fisherman   |

