.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, western, thriller, epic
City: berlin, edinburgh, hannover, marseilles
1. the person traveling to marseilles is the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the person traveling to hannover is the person watching documentary movies##1
3. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person watching epic movies##1
4. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
5. the person watching documentary movies is in an even position##4
6. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | western | documentary | thriller    | epic |
| City   | berlin   | hannover  | marseilles | edinburgh     |

