.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
House: palace, townhouse, craftsman, cape-cod
City: liverpool, rome, paris, prague
1. the craftsman house is on the left of the palace house##1
2. the craftsman house is in an even position##4
3. the person traveling to rome is the craftsman house##1
4. the person traveling to paris is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome##3
5. the person traveling to rome is between the person traveling to prague and the person traveling to paris##2
6. the townhouse house is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| House         | cape-cod   | craftsman | palace | townhouse    |
| City   | paris | rome  | prague     | liverpool |

