.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
4 different games are played: billiard, canasta, bridge, scrabble
City: rome, colone, hamburg, liverpool
1. the person traveling to colone is on the far left##1
2. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
3. the person playing scrabble is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
5. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
6. the person traveling to hamburg is in an even position##4
7. the person traveling to rome is the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Game   | scrabble | billiard    | bridge       | canasta |
| City       | colone  | hamburg | liverpool | rome  |

