.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, lily, iris, bellflower
4 different games are played: snooker, chess, mah-jongg, monopoly
1. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
3. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
4. the person playing chess is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
5. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
6. the person playing snooker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Flower   | lily | iris | aconite  | bellflower |
| Game     | snooker      | mah-jongg       | chess | monopoly     |

