.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, january, august, february
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, brazilian, american, canadian
1. the person who's birthday is in january is in an even position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the spanish##3
3. the brazilian is between the person who's birthday is in november and the spanish##2
4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far left or far right##3
5. the american is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
6. the american is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Birthday         | november | august   | february | january |
| Nationality   | canadian          | brazilian | spanish         | american  |

 